description:
Made for Mini Game Jam #88.

Save your Daughter from an alien Invasion!

Use the arrow keys to steer up and down, to avoid traffic cones and totaled cars!

This was my first game jam project! And because of that, I wasn't quite able to finish it... Expect a full, updated version with a story and more well, game in it, before the end of the year!

Thank you for playing my game! Any and all feedback and criticism  is greatly appreciated :)

If you wanna download, then extract zip and click the file with the alien icon to play!
